Class MCTMutableTreeNode

java.lang.Object
  javax.swing.tree.DefaultMutableTreeNode
      gov.nasa.arc.mct.gui.MCTMutableTreeNode
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, javax.swing.tree.MutableTreeNode, javax.swing.tree.TreeNode
public class MCTMutableTreeNode
extends javax.swing.tree.DefaultMutableTreeNode

A DefaultMutableTreeNode which contains a flag to indicate if a node is just a proxy to its children or actually contains real children.
